@startuml
title Event Systems - High-Level Lifetime Map
skinparam shadowing false

participant Application
participant EventQueue
participant LayerStack
participant CoreLayer
participant EventBus
participant "UI Panels" as UIPanels
participant "Worker Jobs" as WorkerJobs

Application -> EventQueue : owns and drains each frame
Application -> LayerStack : owns and dispatches platform events
Application -> CoreLayer : coordinates runtime services
CoreLayer -> EventBus : owns subsystem bus

UIPanels -> EventBus : Subscribe/Publish
WorkerJobs -> EventBus : Queue(...)
Application -> EventBus : ProcessQueue()

@enduml
